            <title>[PDFBOX-3626] StackOverflowException on a valid PDF</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-3626</link>
                <project id="12310760" key="PDFBOX">PDFBox</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;On the attached document, which opens fine in Acrobat, PDDocument,load() throws a StackOverflowException:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Exception in thread &quot;main&quot; java.lang.StackOverflowError&lt;br/&gt;
