&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-3626&quot; title=&quot;StackOverflowException on a valid PDF&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PDFBOX-3626&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PDFBOX-3626&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: stop brute force search at the last EOF marker to avoid reading garbage attached to the end&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
